  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You plead to a divine entity to protect one of your allies in their time of need. When a creature you can see within range fails a saving throw, you can use your reaction to roll a d20. On a roll of 16 or higher, the divine entity intervenes and the target succeeds on their saving throw instead.</p><p><strong><em>At Higher Levels:</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you reduce the DC by 2 for every slot level above 1st.</p>",
